        "rich_text_A8fUE6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Two Different Diamond Shapes Make the Design Special",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Why Two Different Diamond Shapes Make the Design Special</h2><p>One of the most distinctive features of a Toi et Moi ring is that the two stones don’t have to be identical.</p><p>In fact, many designs intentionally use different diamond shapes or <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/gemstone-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"gemstones \">gemstones </a>to represent individuality.</p><p>Some beautiful combinations include:</p>",
            "custom_id": "why-two",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>1.] Pear and radiant diamonds<br/>2.] Marquise and round diamonds<br/>3.] Emerald and round diamonds<br/><br/>For instance, the Emerald & Round Cut Diamond Toi et Moi Ring combines two contrasting shapes that create visual interest while still feeling balanced.</p><p>These combinations allow the ring to reflect the idea that two people can be different yet perfectly matched.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Toi et Moi Rings Often Combine Diamonds and Gemstones",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Toi et Moi Rings Often Combine Diamonds and Gemstones</h2><p>Another modern interpretation of the Toi et Moi design includes mixing diamonds with coloured gemstones.</p><p>This variation adds personality and symbolism to the ring.</p><p>For example:</p>",
            "custom_id": "toi-et",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>1.] One stone might represent a birthstone.<br/>2.] A coloured gemstone might reflect personal style.<br/>3.] The second stone may remain a classic diamond.<br/><br/>The Diamond & Gemstone Toi et Moi Ring and Blue and Pink Gemstone & Diamond Toi et Moi Ring from Lucira show how combining stones can create something truly unique.</p><p>These designs feel expressive while still carrying the traditional meaning of the ring.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ry4cQt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text ",
          "settings": {
