        "rich_text_MmQE44": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lucira’s Approach to Toi et Moi Ring Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lucira’s Approach to Toi et Moi Ring Design</h2><p>At Lucira Jewelry, Toi et Moi rings are designed to celebrate individuality and connection. Each piece highlights two stones that complement each other while maintaining balance and elegance.</p><p>Lucira rings feature IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, ensuring brilliance along with responsible sourcing. From classic diamond pairings to gemstone combinations, each design reflects the idea of two unique elements coming together beautifully.</p><p>Whether it’s the Marquise and Emerald Toi et Moi Engagement Ring or the Pear & Radiant Cut Diamond Toi et Moi Ring, Lucira’s collection captures the timeless symbolism of this romantic style.</p>",
            "custom_id": "approach",
